---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Clients" description="Missions et cas clients — Julien Lacaze, CMO Freelance B2B">

  <!-- Header -->
  <section id="clients-header" style="
    padding: 12rem 3rem 6rem;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  ">
    <span class="tag">Clients</span>
    <h1 style="
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      line-height: 1.05;
    ">
      Ce que j'ai<br/>
      <em style="color: var(--color-accent); font-style: italic;">vraiment</em> fait.
    </h1>
    <p style="
      color: var(--color-muted);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    ">
      Découvrez les missions B2B sur lesquelles je suis intervenu récemment. Économie circulaire, droit, formation...
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Cases -->
  <section style="
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 3rem;
  ">

    <!-- Case 1 : Noé -->
    <article id="noe" class="case-study" style="
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: 6rem;
      align-items: start;
    ">
      <div class="case-study-left reveal-left" style="position: sticky; top: 8rem;">
        <div style="
          font-family: var(--font-display);
          font-size: 4rem;
          color: var(--color-border);
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
          line-height: 1;
        ">01</div>
        <img src="/logos/noe.png" alt="Noé" style="height: 40px; width: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;" />
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Noé</h2>
        <span class="tag">CMO Part-time</span>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Secteur</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Formation / Enseignement</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Rythme</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">2 jours / semaine</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Date</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">2025–2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Le contexte</p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-muted);">
            <!-- À compléter avec ton vrai brief -->
            Noé est la formation n°1 de Product Manager en France.
            Un bootcamp de 4 semaines qui permet d'apprendre en profondeur le métier de Product Manager.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ce que j'ai fait</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Garant de la stratégie d'acquisition digitale : campagnes paid, SEO, contenu, email, social
            </li>
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Pilotage et collaboration avec les agences externes (SEO / SEA)
            </li>
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Lancement d'opérations growth
            </li>
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Management d'une personne
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>


    <!-- Case 2 : SNCF -->
    <article id="sncf" class="case-study" style="
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: 6rem;
      align-items: start;
    ">
      <div class="case-study-left reveal-left" style="position: sticky; top: 8rem;">
        <div style="
          font-family: var(--font-display);
          font-size: 4rem;
          color: var(--color-border);
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
          line-height: 1;
        ">02</div>
        <img src="/logos/sncf.png" alt="SNCF" style="height: 40px; width: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;" />
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">SNCF</h2>
        <span class="tag">Conseil</span>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Secteur</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Transport / Ferroviaire</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Lieu</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Distanciel</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Date</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Oct 2025 – Mars 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Le contexte</p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-muted);">
            Migration du bilan carbone de SNCF Numérique Responsable vers le logiciel SaaS de comptabilité carbone Sweep.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ce que j'ai fait</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Migration du bilan carbone de SNCF Numérique Responsable vers le logiciel SaaS de comptabilité carbone Sweep
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>


    <!-- Case 3 : Coédis Impact -->
    <article id="coedis" class="case-study" style="
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: 6rem;
      align-items: start;
    ">
      <div class="case-study-left reveal-left" style="position: sticky; top: 8rem;">
        <div style="
          font-family: var(--font-display);
          font-size: 4rem;
          color: var(--color-border);
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
          line-height: 1;
        ">03</div>
        <img src="/logos/coedis.png" alt="Coédis" style="height: 40px; width: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;" />
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Coédis</h2>
        <span class="tag">Email marketing</span>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Secteur</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">BTP / Gros oeuvre</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Format</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Convention B2B · 500 pers.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Lieu</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Distanciel</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Date</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Avril 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Le contexte</p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-muted);">
            Déploiement de la stratégie d'email marketing dans le cadre
            de la 1ère grande convention B2B (Coédis Impact) de la Fédération
            des Distributeurs professionnels spécialisés.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ce que j'ai fait</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Stratégie d'email marketing B2B
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>


    <!-- Case 3 : Alexia.fr -->
    <article id="alexia" class="case-study" style="
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: 6rem;
      align-items: start;
    ">
      <div class="case-study-left reveal-left" style="position: sticky; top: 8rem;">
        <div style="
          font-family: var(--font-display);
          font-size: 4rem;
          color: var(--color-border);
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
          line-height: 1;
        ">04</div>
        <img src="/logos/alexia.png" alt="Alexia.fr" style="height: 40px; width: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;" />
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Alexia.fr</h2>
        <span class="tag">Copywriting</span>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Secteur</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Droit</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Lieu</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Distanciel</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Date</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Novembre 2025</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Le contexte</p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-muted);">
            Copywriting des pages business du site alexia.fr
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ce que j'ai fait</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Copywriting du funnel d'inscription du site alexia.fr, page d'accueil, page divorce à l'amiable
            </li>
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Collaboration avec la personne chargée de la refonte UX / UI
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>


    <!-- Case 4 : Geev -->
    <article id="geev" class="case-study" style="
      padding: 6rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: 6rem;
      align-items: start;
    ">
      <div class="case-study-left reveal-left" style="position: sticky; top: 8rem;">
        <div style="
          font-family: var(--font-display);
          font-size: 4rem;
          color: var(--color-border);
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
          line-height: 1;
        ">05</div>
        <img src="/logos/geev.png" alt="Geev" style="height: 40px; width: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; opacity: 0.9;" />
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Geev</h2>
        <span class="tag">Marketing B2B</span>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Secteur</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Économie circulaire</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Lieu</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Présentiel</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Date</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Sept 2024 – Mai 2025</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Le contexte</p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-muted);">
            Développement du marketing des offres B2B de Geev Pro :
            reprise par le don, comptes pro Geev.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ce que j'ai fait</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Lancement de campagnes cold emailing
            </li>
            <li style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-muted);">
              <span style="color: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem;">—</span>
              Suivi et lancement des nouveaux comptes pro B2B
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section id="clients-cta" style="
    padding: 8rem 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  ">
    <h2 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      Vous voulez en faire partie ?
    </h2>
    <a href="/#contact" style="
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--color-accent);
      color: var(--color-bg);
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-radius: 1px;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    ">Me contacter</a>
  </section>

</Layout>
